blueprint.description:
Important:
If you are building without water mods, before placing the main tile, be sure to place this landfill first.

To add to top: overlap the bottom 4 offshore pumps with pumps of existing tile (on top).

To add to bottom: overlap the 4 teeth of landfill with bottom two rows of pumps of existing tile.
blueprint.label: Tilable 2x6 landfill
